---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About FetchPicks" description="Learn about FetchPicks - who we are, what we do, and why you can trust our pet product reviews.">
  <article style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">About FetchPicks</h1>
    
    <section style="margin-top: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Our Mission</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        FetchPicks was created with one simple goal: <strong>help pet owners make better buying decisions.</strong>
        The pet market is flooded with thousands of products-some great, some mediocre, and some that aren't worth your money.
        We cut through the noise and give you honest, data-driven recommendations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 28px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">How We Review</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Every product we recommend goes through a rigorous evaluation process:
      </p>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li><strong>Ingredient Analysis</strong> - We scrutinize labels, sourcing, and nutritional profiles.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer Research</strong> - We analyze thousands of real customer reviews to identify patterns.</li>
        <li><strong>Expert Consultation</strong> - We reference veterinary guidelines and industry standards.</li>
        <li><strong>Value Assessment</strong> - We compare price vs. quality to find the best value options.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 28px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Transparency</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        FetchPicks participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. This means that if you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase,
        we may earn a small commission-<strong>at no extra cost to you.</strong> This commission helps us maintain the site and continue producing great content.
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        Importantly: <strong>our recommendations are never influenced by commissions.</strong> We only recommend products we genuinely believe in,
        regardless of commission rates. If a product isn't worth buying, we'll tell you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 28px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Contact</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        Have a question, suggestion, or product you'd like us to review? We'd love to hear from you.
        Reach out at <strong>hello@fetchpicks.com</strong>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
